headline: Fox Corporation Chief Financial Officer Steve Tomsic to Participate in Upcoming Barclays Communications and Content Symposium
summary: Fox Corporation (Nasdaq: FOXA, FOX) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Steve Tomsic will participate in the upcoming Barclays Communications and Content Symposium on February 25, at approximately 10:25am (Eastern), 7:25am (Pacific).
